      *
     C           KEY1      SETLLAJSPL921
      *  ﾅﾎﾞﾎｦbﾓ ﾛﾃｰnﾞ CLR
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    OP
     C                     MOVE *ZERO     @KIBN
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    @TEHI
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    @PAG1
