     C                     MOVE J5ZBR2    #ZAI2
     C                     MOVE J5CTRK    #CTRK
     C                     MOVE J5CTRD    #CTRD
     C                     MOVE J5SPNK    #SPNK
     C                     MOVE J5SPND    #SPND
